title: #92Noon! Montage/Bailey/Bercich/Siny/JG
description: Vikings win! Montage, kicker Dan Bailey calls in and Pete Bercich sits in studio for hardcore football analysis. Dave Sinykin offers thoughts on the Packers losing, talkers/calls, and Justin Gaard wraps show with Gophers football reaction.
